<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        /* Define your CSS styles inline */
        .bdy {
            background-color: #262626;
            padding: 21px 16px;
            height: max-content;
        }

        .bdy-content {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 23px;
        }

        .bdy p, .bdy ul {
            font-family: "Darker Grotesque", sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #FFFFFF;
        }

        .bdy h2 {
            font-family: "Darker Grotesque", sans-serif;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #FFFFFF;
        }

        .bdy h1 {
            font-family: "Darker Grotesque", sans-serif;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #FFFFFF;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <main class="main">
        <div class="bdy" style="background-color: #262626; display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
            <div class="bdy-content" style="display: block;">
                <div class="logo">
                    <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dwl0pqzlx/image/upload/v1712586316/Frame_5_objfql.png" alt="">
                </div>
                <h2 style="font-family: 'Darker Grotesque', sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 900; color: #FFFFFF;">Successful Registration for Coal-City Half Marathon</h2>

                <h1 style="font-family: 'Darker Grotesque', sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 900; color: #FFFFFF;">Dear [Participant's Name],</h1>
                <p style="font-family: 'Darker Grotesque', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #FFFFFF;">Congratulations! We are delighted to confirm that your registration for the Coal-City Half Marathon has been successfully processed.</p>

                <div>
                    <p style="font-family: 'Darker Grotesque', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #FFFFFF;">Registration Details:</p>
                    <ul style="font-family: 'Darker Grotesque', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #FFFFFF;">
                        <li>Event Name: Coal-City Half Marathon</li>
                        <li>Date: [Event Date]</li>
                        <li>Location: [Event Location]</li>
                        <li>Registration ID: [XXXXXXX]</li>
                        <li>Category: [e.g., Half Marathon, Fun Run, etc.]</li>
                        <li>Participant Name: [Participant's Full Name]</li>
                        <li>Contact Number: [Participant's Contact Number]</li>
                        <li>Email Address: [Participant's Email Address]</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <p style="font-family: 'Darker Grotesque', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #FFFFFF;">Please keep this email for your records. If you have any questions regarding your registration, feel free to contact us at [Customer Support Email] or [Customer Support Phone Number]. We look forward to seeing you at the starting line!</p>

                <p style="font-family: 'Darker Grotesque', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #FFFFFF;">Warm Regards,<br>[Your Name] [Event Organizer/Company Name]</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
